oc:kn_d874d44b a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:OutputFormat ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating contract review output" ;
    oc:directiveContent """## Risk Assessment
### 🔴/🟡/🟢 [Severity] Risk Items
#### N. [Risk Title] (Section X.X)
- **Issue**: [description]
- **Impact**: [consequence]
- **Recommendation**: [action]

## Key Terms Summary
| Term | Value | Risk |

## Recommendations
### Must Fix (before signing):
- [items]""" ;
